n a plate to keep warm."},{"content":"Add cream and cook <b>5 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add yoghurt, salt and white pepper and blend <b>30 sec\/speed 10<b>. Remove salmon from parcel, transfer to a serving dish, sprinkle salmon with parsley and serve hot, with sauce and vegetables on the side."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Here’s a fast and easy meal that is original and flavourful. The spice rub gives the tender salmon a kick, which is tempered by the slightly sweet curried mango sauce and fresh vegetables. As always, adjust spices and vegetables to your liking."],"basicInfo":["easy","35m","1h","4 portions"]}